headline: THE FQ'S AI SUMMIT RETURNS NOVEMBER 12, 2025 TO NYC
summary: The Female Quotient (The FQ) will host their second annual AI Summit on Wednesday, November 12, 2025 at Webster Hall in New York City. Building on the success of the 2024 inaugural program, the summit expands this year into a full-day experience, convening senior executives, marketers, operators, and creators across marketing, media, technology, and entertainment, for practical conversations, live demonstrations, collaboration, and case studies that put AI to work.

headline: Infinitus Partners with Outshift by Cisco to Advance Interoperability and Trust Among AI Agents
summary: Infinitus Systems, healthcare's leading agentic communications partner powering more than 100 million minutes of clinical and administrative conversations, today announced that the company has partnered with Outshift by Cisco to streamline healthcare operations, leveraging the orchestration layer of discoverable, secure, and distributed AI agents in healthcare.
